Designed, modeled, and 3D printed a fully interactive life-sized prop replica of the Pack-a-Punched Sally from Call of Duty Zombies, engineering a complete electronics suite from the ground up encompassing a battery-powered microcontroller, RGB color-changing LEDs, trigger-activated button mechanics, integrated speakers, and hidden easter eggs. Developed a companion Wi-Fi application enabling users to upload custom sounds and define their own easter egg interactions, elevating the prop from a static replica into a fully programmable, user-customizable interactive experience.